<div class="header-bar">How It Works</div>
<h3>What is spotsaving ?</h3>
<p>It is a public platform for local communities and businesses to share deals/great prices  in their city,
as well as discover items on clearance/sale from their local stores, </p>
<h3>Local Businesses </h3>
<p>If you are a local business, sign up and don't forget to check "Are you a Retailer" checkbox.Then click Retailer and kindly list your deal or special you offer and we will advertise locally  for you free of charge.Yes it is <span style="color:red">FREE.</span> </p>
<h3>Ask your local community how much and where to find what</h3>
<p>This is the great and easy way to discover deals in your city.Simply fill in the product or service you are looking for and check atleast one the checkboxes.<br><b>Note:It is very important you include brand and size to get the best response, if you are asking about an item</b></p>
<h3>Tell us the deal you saw at the store</h3>
<p>Simply share with your community about an item or service on sale/clearence you came across at your local store.
<b><i>(Note:It is very important you include item brand and size for clarity</i></b>)For each item/deal you list, people in your community will be able to vote for it, whether they think it is a great deal(vote thumbs up) or not(vote thumbs down). If they vote up you will earn points, if they vote down you will lose points
Active sharing from you will inspire others in your community to share deals that they see at their local stores therefore building a largest network of deals and discovery for your own city. </p>
<h3>Why vote thumbs up?</h3>
<p>Vote thumbs up for deals that you really think are great deals and ones that have enough details describing the particular product and terms of that particular deal. Deals with a high number of votes will appear on the front page</p>

<h3>Why vote thumbs down?</h3>
<p>You can vote thumbs down if the deal contains the following<br/>
<b>Note:</b><br/>Before voting, it is important to let the author of the post know about the issue by posting a reply comment first 
<ul>
<li>It is not really a great deal (price mentioned is a regular price)</li> 
<li>There is not enough information on the deal e.g no proper explaination how that deal works  </li>
<li>There is alot of typos on the deal presentation,to the point that it could mislead people</li>
<li>It does not include item brand, size or the location mentioned is wrong</li>
</ul>
